Hmmm.... Parked your wizard already? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/30/01 5:45:12 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://wots-signatures.hypermart.net/rombus/sidepic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dissed by my own guild...</span><hr size=1> Again, I grouped in DL and Wizards like to nuke.  They often complain 'OOM.'  /shrug<br>
